    "TitleKey": "Covalex_HaulCargo_SingleToMulti_title",
    "DisplayTitle": "Experienced Rank - Medium Cargo Haul",
    "Description": "Hey,\n\nThe folks at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> have what I like to call a \u201cpilot\u2019s special\u201d waiting to be distributed - a haul of quantum fuel, hydrogen fuel, and ship ammo. Load it up from a freight elevator and deliver it to the following spots in whatever order works best for you. Expect the containers to all be <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize)</EM4> or smaller.   \n\nDROP OFF LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER)\n\n~mission(SingleToMultiToken) \n\nBy the way, we strongly encourage contractors to bring a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> along.   \n\n~mission(Contractor|SignOff)\n\nChase Hewitt\nJr. Logistics Coordinator\nCovalex Shipping  \n'Anything you need, anywhere you need it.'\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCovalex Shipping is a limited liability corporation. To encourage timely deliveries and prevent fraud on cargo hauls, Covalex Shipping will set a delivery time limit and upon expiration, any undelivered cargo will be considered stolen and treated as such. Total payment will be prorated according to the percentage of cargo successfully delivered.",
    "DescriptionKey": "Covalex_HaulCargo_SingleToMulti_Processed_Mixed_QTFuelHydroFuelShipAmmo",
    "DisplayDescription": "Hey,\n\nThe folks at <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4> have what I like to call a \u201cpilot\u2019s special\u201d waiting to be distributed - a haul of quantum fuel, hydrogen fuel, and ship ammo. Load it up from a freight elevator and deliver it to the following spots in whatever order works best for you. Expect the containers to all be <EM4>16 SCU</EM4> or smaller.   \n\nDROP OFF LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER)\n\n- Freight elevator at <EM4>[Destination|Address]</EM4>\n- Freight elevator at <EM4>[Destination1|Address]</EM4> \n\nBy the way, we strongly encourage contractors to bring a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> along.   \n\n[Contractor|SignOff]\n\nChase Hewitt\nJr. Logistics Coordinator\nCovalex Shipping  \n'Anything you need, anywhere you need it.'\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCovalex Shipping is a limited liability corporation. To encourage timely deliveries and prevent fraud on cargo hauls, Covalex Shipping will set a delivery time limit and upon expiration, any undelivered cargo will be considered stolen and treated as such. Total payment will be prorated according to the percentage of cargo successfully delivered.",
